des: The skill "Sites de Paris" provides touristic information and some details about sites : Attractions and Monuments of Paris. This skill can be used on several Devices with displays such as Echo Show and Echo Spot (to display images and interact with) thanks to support of APL (Amazon Presentation Language), combining interaction multimodal (voice and screen)
